Author: _fidgetspinner
Text: yes, i so relate! my lyft driver a few days ago was asking me what i eat/cook, and i was like "uhhh i mean, i eat a lot of protein bars, apples, uhh stuff like that i guess..." he was like "no like what kind of FOOD do you eat?" i replied, "i mean, that's pretty much what i usually eat..." SO AWKWARD. he was seriously so confused.
